'''''Bangladesher Samajtantrik Dal''''' ('Socialist Party of Bangladesh', often referred to as '''BASAD''') is a [[communist party]] in [[Bangladesh]]. The party was founded on 7 November 1980.<ref>[http://www.spb.org.bd/history.html SPB :: History<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> BASAD is led by Khalequzzaman.<ref>[http://www.sananews.com.pk/news.php?netwire=2613&cwire=8 EC dialogue with political parties from Sept 12 - South Asian News Agency, Accurate & Reliable<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

